	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="8" facs="R 87-11 17 (35)"/>
			<p><!--Samuel W. Honaker, Transmitting Bulgarian Anti-Jewish Law of August 29, 1942, with Comments, Istanbul, 16.11.1942, S. 8. Records of the Department of State relating to internal affairs of Bulgaria 1910-1944, Washington 1982 (Mikrofilm-Edition): Dokument 874.4016/???.--></p>
			<p>„Reports received from <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/727011/sofia.html">Sofia</placeName> on <date when="1942-11-13">November
					13, 1942</date>, indicate that this <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-335" type="subject">law</term>
				is being rigorously enforced. Previous reports that there was some lenity in the enforcement of the law applied only to a small number
				of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-804" type="subject">Christian Jews</term> with regard to wearing the
					<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-338" type="subject">Star of David</term>. Also some postponement was
				found necessary due to the physical impossibility of moving so many <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864"
					type="subject">Jews</term> into the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-545" type="subject"
					>ghetto</term> or <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">deporting</term> them at one
				time. A prominent <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1427" type="subject">Jewish surgeon</term> arrived in
					<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/745044/istanbul.html">Istanbul</placeName> from<placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/727011/sofia.html"> Sofia</placeName> on <date when="1942-11-12">November 12</date> after having been
					<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-608" type="subject">deprived of his right to practice his
					profession</term>. He owned and operated a <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-870" type="subject"
					>hospital and clinic</term>, which is forbidden to <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864"
					type="subject">Jews</term> in accordance with Article 33 of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-335"
					type="subject">Law</term>. All his <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-585" type="subject"
					>property</term> was taken away from him. Actually this man is a <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-767">Catholic</term> and has been such for thirty-five years. He declared
				that the reason for his severe treatment is the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-813" type="subject"
					>jealousy</term> of <term ref="#ehri_dr_nationalities_bulgarians">Bulgarian</term>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-287" type="subject">surgeons and doctors</term> who take this means of
				ridding themselves of competition.</p>
			<p>As has already been mentioned several thousand <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject"
					>Jews</term> are now in the process of being <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject"
					>deported</term> from <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/727011/sofia.html">Sofia</placeName>. Where they will be sent is not
				known. They are supposed to be <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">deported</term> to
				towns and villages in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/732800/republic-of-bulgaria.html">Bulgaria</placeName> but some high
				placed persons believe many of them will be <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject"
					>deported</term> to <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">Poland</placeName>. Some think they
				will be put in <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-496" type="subject">concentration camps</term> inside of
					<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/search.html?q=bulgarien&amp;country=">Bulgaria</placeName> where many will eventually die
				of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-292" type="subject">disease</term> and <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-569" type="subject">starvation</term>. Others, including the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1427" type="subject">surgeon</term> referred to above, think that a large
				proportion of them will be <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-541" type="subject">shot</term>, as they have
				been in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/792680/belgrade.html">Belgrade</placeName> and other cities. In any case, the content
				of the law, together with the severity with which it is being enforced show that its purpose is the complete destruction of the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-872" type="subject">Jewish community</term> in <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/727011/sofia.html">Sofia</placeName>.“</p>
